title: Paneer Tikka Masala
description: Paneer cubes marinated in a blend of yogurt and spices, grilled to perfection, and served in a creamy tomato-based gravy with hints of cumin and coriander. A must-try vegetarian dish full of flavors.

title: Cheeseburger
description: A juicy beef patty topped with melted cheddar cheese, lettuce, tomatoes, onions, and pickles. Served in a toasted bun with ketchup and mustard, this classic cheeseburger offers a mouth-watering experience.

title: Peking Duck
description: Peking Duck is a famous Chinese dish that involves roasting a whole duck until the skin is crispy and golden brown. The meat is sliced and served with thin pancakes, hoisin sauce, and sliced cucumbers.

title: Tandoori Chicken
description: Chicken marinated in a mixture of yogurt and spices, then cooked in a traditional clay oven (tandoor) until tender. The smoky flavor combined with the rich spices makes this dish a true delight.

title: Fish Tacos
description: Crispy fried fish fillets, topped with shredded cabbage, cilantro, and a zesty lime sauce, all wrapped in a soft tortilla. These tacos offer a refreshing and flavorful experience perfect for seafood lovers.

title: Margherita Pizza
description: A simple yet flavorful pizza topped with fresh mozzarella, tomatoes, and basil leaves. Baked to perfection in a wood-fired oven, this pizza has a crispy crust and a delicious, fresh topping combination.

title: Pad Thai
description: A popular Thai stir-fried noodle dish made with shrimp, tofu, eggs, and peanuts. The dish is flavored with tamarind paste, fish sauce, and lime juice, offering a perfect balance of sweet, sour, and savory tastes.

title: Butter Chicken
description: Tender chicken pieces cooked in a rich, creamy tomato gravy with a blend of Indian spices. This dish is best enjoyed with naan or basmati rice for a flavorful and satisfying meal.

title: Falafel Wrap
description: A wrap filled with crispy falafel balls, fresh vegetables, and a creamy tahini sauce. The combination of flavors and textures makes this a satisfying and healthy meal on the go.

title: Spaghetti Carbonara
description: A classic Italian pasta dish made with eggs, cheese, pancetta, and black pepper. The creamy texture of the sauce pairs perfectly with the al dente spaghetti for a simple yet indulgent meal.

title: Lamb Shawarma
description: Slices of marinated lamb slow-cooked on a vertical rotisserie and served in a flatbread with garlic sauce, pickles, and fresh vegetables. The spices and tender lamb make this a flavorful street food favorite.

title: Beef Wellington
description: Tender beef fillet coated with mushroom duxelles, wrapped in puff pastry, and baked to a golden brown. A luxurious and iconic British dish, served with a rich red wine sauce.

title: Dim Sum Platter
description: A selection of bite-sized dim sum, including shrimp dumplings, pork buns, and vegetable spring rolls. Served with soy sauce and chili dipping sauces, perfect for a light and flavorful appetizer.

title: Fettuccine Alfredo
description: A creamy pasta dish made with fettuccine noodles tossed in a rich sauce of butter, Parmesan cheese, and cream. This Italian classic is indulgent and comforting, best enjoyed with garlic bread.

title: Tom Yum Soup
description: A hot and sour Thai soup, made with shrimp, lemongrass, lime juice, fish sauce, and chili peppers. This flavorful broth is both refreshing and spicy, offering a perfect balance of tastes.

title: Greek Salad
description: A fresh and colorful salad made with tomatoes, cucumbers, red onions, Kalamata olives, and feta cheese. Dressed with olive oil and oregano, this dish is a light and healthy option.

title: Miso Soup
description: A traditional Japanese soup made from dashi broth, miso paste, tofu, seaweed, and green onions. The umami flavors of the miso are comforting and make for a perfect start to any meal.

title: BBQ Ribs
description: Juicy and tender pork ribs, slow-cooked and basted with a smoky BBQ sauce. Served with coleslaw and cornbread, these ribs are fall-off-the-bone delicious, perfect for any BBQ lover.

title: Shakshuka
description: Juicy and tender pork ribs, slow-cooked and basted with a smoky BBQ sauce. Served with coleslaw and cornbread, these ribs are fall-off-the-bone delicious, perfect for any BBQ lover.

title: Chicken Caesar Salad
description: Grilled chicken breast served on a bed of fresh romaine lettuce, tossed with Caesar dressing, croutons, and Parmesan cheese. A light yet flavorful salad, perfect for lunch or dinner.

title: Buffalo Wings

title: Vegan Buddha Bowl

title: Margarita

title: Tempura

title: Ceviche
